      • findNearestPoint

        public static meico.supplementary.KeyValue<java.awt.Point,​java.lang.Double> findNearestPoint​(java.util.ArrayList<java.awt.Point> pointCloud,
                                                                                                   java.awt.Point pivot)
        this method implements a brute force approach to finding the nearest point in a hashmap of points
        Parameters:
        pointCloud - the point cloud as hashmap, so we can return the key object as reference to the point
        pivot - the pivotal point for which we seek the nearest in the hashmap
        Returns:
        a tuple of the point's key and distance, if there are more than one nearest points only the first is returned
